           move      rf-ocr-dcn-cnf       to   srt-dcn-cnf            .
           move      d-qev-roc-qta-dev    to   srt-qta-dev            .
           move      rf-dcp-alf-pro       to   srt-alf-mag            .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
