      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-buf-ass-wqu    to   w-bas-qta-ass
                                              (w-bas-num-ele)         .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Data assegnata                      *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-bds-dat-dsp
                    (w-bds-ctr-002)       to   w-bas-dat-ass
                                              (w-bas-num-ele)         .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Protocollo ordine fornitore         *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-bds-prt-orf
                    (w-bds-ctr-002)       to   w-bas-prt-orf
                                              (w-bas-num-ele)         .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Progressivo riga ordine fornitore   *
